{
  "texts": [
    "Message Passing Neural Networks in Papillon et al. (2023b)), our work provides broad coverage of TDA integration into various DL pipelines and architectures.",
    "We did our best to choose work that has a historical and linear connection with deep learning approaches to improve understandability.",
    "This survey provides the broader machine learning community with a convenient starting point to explore how TDA has been integrated with deep learning.",
    "Such interaction brings novel perspectives, benefits, and challenges.",
    "We shed light on the benefits of this interaction demonstrated by the growing adoption of TDA in various deep learning applications."
  ]
}